WEBVTT

00:00.535 --> 00:01.972
Are you guys ready for the next big thing?

00:02.167 --> 00:02.765
Yeah!

00:05.808 --> 00:06.071
What?

00:06.311 --> 00:07.035
Call me crazy.

00:07.801 --> 00:09.292
Can a watch make a phone call?

00:09.563 --> 00:10.164
No!

00:10.301 --> 00:11.494
Can a watch take a picture?

00:11.816 --> 00:12.147
No!

00:12.253 --> 00:12.658
What's that?

00:12.831 --> 00:14.192
I'm getting a call from Mrs. Claus.

00:15.093 --> 00:15.737
Hey, sweetie.

00:15.831 --> 00:16.115
Hi.

00:16.209 --> 00:17.701
Can a watch do all these?

00:17.807 --> 00:18.305
It's not a watch!

00:18.386 --> 00:19.023
What did you just say?

00:19.083 --> 00:19.463
It's not a watch!

00:19.549 --> 00:20.385
Say it again!

00:20.551 --> 00:21.336
It's not a watch!

00:21.402 --> 00:22.107
It's a miracle.

00:24.400 --> 00:28.789
The Galaxy Gear. Now also available for the Galaxy S4, S3 and Note 2.

